| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1176 — Recovery Inhibition (direwolf)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27ef8db1-0f50-53b4-b7fa-6b7994b6aac3"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
